EHLO
250 Hi
MAIL FROM
250 OK
RCPT TO
250 OK
QUIT
221 Bye
****
exim -bs
helo test
mail from:<userx@ok.example>
rcpt to:<usery@broken.example>
quit
****
# A final check that the cache works for sender address
exim -bs
helo test
